description: This file declares internal functions related to TLS Session Entry management for a specific component in the project. It includes function prototypes for managing session states and matching session identities used internally within the TLS implementation.

methods.name: TlsSeoGetSessionState
methods.description: Retrieves the current session state for the TLS session entry.

methods.name: TlsSeoSetSessionState
methods.description: Sets the session state for the TLS session entry.

methods.name: TlsSeoReset
methods.description: Resets the TLS session entry to its initial state.

methods.name: TlsSeoMatch1
methods.description: Matches a session based on host and peer IDs and connection end.

methods.name: TlsSeoMatch2
methods.description: Matches a session based on host ID, peer ID, and session ID.
